    <user>dimstar_suse</user>
    <comment>Nice little application for Django projects providing fixtures
and models for a &quot;complete&quot; list of world countries and US states.
Also throwing in a small template filter for getting country flags by
ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code.</comment>
